{"tid":185914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去中國銀行櫃員機撳六千蚊, 畀佢食咗, 重扣埋數","createTime":"2017-04-03T20:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T16:47:59.000Z","uid":71949,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5977f7261bc0c45eda9027e33f81bedba5d1a0c2","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:17:40.000Z","msg":"本身好開心啱啱知道自己出咗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去樓下中國銀行櫃員機嗰度撳錢撳咗六千蚊，等咗幾分鐘都未出到錢，之後佢就顯示話線路繁忙請稍後再試咁，我又不以為意啦，又冇攞收據出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後點知佢真係扣鳩咗我六千蚊而家都唔知點算好聽日又公眾假期,好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以俾啲意見我， 打去銀行佢又講埋啲廢話叫我公眾假期之後自己去銀行報失， 而家好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948d9cdd2ebf621dd18ddd049ad8294f58e316f9","tid":185914,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:28:33.000Z","msg":"放心啦，一定會比返你<br />\n佢地無啦啦多左錢都好頭痕"},{"pid":"d5454490289493f7ce434ed94bde353bbfaf1504","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T20:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心啦，一定會比返你<br />\n佢地無啦啦多左錢都好頭痕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打<br />\n香港地賺錢一分一毫咬出嚟都係有血有汗更何況六千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cecf9216cd2742b49f06b4d5044e5640f2d915","tid":185914,"uid":16804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T21:21:25.000Z","msg":"去銀行同佢講囉 快則一個禮拜 慢則一個月 中銀某d ATM機好似外判"},{"pid":"21eb3415a30a245a678625f222ea0263c7f19a6d","tid":185914,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T21:24:56.000Z","msg":"差唔多情況 又係中銀<br />\n試過用櫃員機入10000 <br />\n但入左之後户口顯示無入到<br />\n同職員講返 抄返身分證 <br />\n過多幾日就靜靜雞入返比我"},{"pid":"ba8f221de29d166d372645d9501c342d21739d62","tid":185914,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T22:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>放心啦，一定會比返你<br />\n佢地無啦啦多左錢都好頭痕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝巴打<br />\n香港地賺錢一分一毫咬出嚟都係有血有汗更何況六千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做趙雲都咁冇品 預左啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打去同職員講番 多數一星期到就比番錢你"},{"pid":"07ac83e62ce968b946d11c45a96e85224f86ef2f","tid":185914,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:43:55.000Z","msg":"有次禁完500唔記得拎 過幾日退返比我"},{"pid":"7534a128c9740bd5a8df6dcc61b425eb685dd092","tid":185914,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"渣打試過會比番你， 仲話唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那銀行就唔知喇"},{"pid":"9668f792d06f4724c0d7495679182817a5938451","tid":185914,"uid":42250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T01:51:57.000Z","msg":"即場打999"},{"pid":"f328d51a8da39e467f3e2541433d54e795b59899","tid":185914,"uid":11914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"張提款卡後面未有電話係24小時架，打去同客戶主任講就得， 佢會問你幾點邊度食卡<br />\n<br />\n利申比人食過3次"},{"pid":"3d1a80bccd8d7aef922cd7e988843889343c1a28","tid":185914,"uid":6116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"有蔽路電視架 你去分行搞就ok"},{"pid":"94b88074f30a82e8ce3357e63970235abb1ce73f","tid":185914,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"銀行無啦啦多左錢搞亂條數<br />\n佢仲驚過你 放心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea265e09243fb1cd936b5dd87b33a06c71ba789","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去銀行同佢講囉 快則一個禮拜 慢則一個月 中銀某d ATM機好似外判</blockquote><br />\