><br />\n<br />\n講真如果唔係公司要用支那銀行根本就完全唔想 涉及 支那既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58405a742676d019a7458073e72e61b23e03423b","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即場打999</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有打去，madam都係嗰句，最好打去銀行，實際作用其實都唔係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd94e9b3d051b08ac0cedfc0dc57c7e3be45c972","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:51:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張提款卡後面未有電話係24小時架，打去同客戶主任講就得， 佢會問你幾點邊度食卡<br />\n<br />\n利申比人食過3次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n尋晚我搵部支那機都搵唔到熱線電話，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有打去24小時熱線不過都係喺度推莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都係答要等公眾假期之後佢地先可以幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b3aac0a8d7dcb0f2c71f455fb39451e245f035","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有蔽路電視架 你去分行搞就ok</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n突然間覺得有閉路電視真係一件好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbb14a4c91bb625ae684134f0fc4a8c79e4e6ac","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>銀行無啦啦多左錢搞亂條數<br />\n佢仲驚過你 放心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望佢會驚過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c05c27c5ebae4997878ef9b5a7b5ebf6d3f302c","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T02:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去銀行填form 就得 佢有閉路又剩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過要等成日，真係好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12c77e2e1f34ff90086e07db2ecd589ba382ded","tid":185914,"uid":92194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"試過用入錢機俾佢食咗<br />\n入咗錢話交易失敗<br />\n但唔退返岀嚟<br />\n打去叫佢搞<br />\n點知幾日後只係俾返一半我<br />\n再打去問佢先俾返另一半我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過係滙豐"},{"pid":"34da290d6f689e5d5183fb8ea19aebc539f289e3","tid":185914,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"有冇即時向 ATM 部 CCTV 舉中指屌柒機入邊嗰個員工呀"},{"pid":"d512e22c606360049c6312813253d710c38bedf9","tid":185914,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有次禁完500唔記得拎 過幾日退返比我</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁好?你有冇打去銀行或者去分行搞或者報警?</blockquote><br />\n我既錢自己拎返有咩咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有打去 佢同我講話會自動check到多左就會退返比我囉 因為冇拎到錢部機會自己食返"},{"pid":"041213221757f5e5fd649fed6114c8c150e099e8","tid":185914,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:15:16.000Z","msg":"用中銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新腥港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a4f6f90d917bc9a4d3bbc99a6225113cac1710","tid":185914,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"上黎問不如google吓啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懶撚過豬"},{"pid":"b644615877e64e5849f99e98f562791d8bb2f2df","tid":185914,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"用支那銀行 唔食曬你結餘咪算好"},{"pid":"b4bdd5b9c6c04fcb1b3bd8816fea8edf439d2bfe","tid":185914,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:22:45.000Z","msg":"我都試過佢都比返你"},{"pid":"9bd7155faf38fad0c47