es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bc1476048d369e6db86ed8e13845271e94e1c4","tid":185914,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:52:29.000Z","msg":"咁都要驚<br />\n係咪鄉下落黎"},{"pid":"ea674e652ed24fa41b2d20f69abadbd3f8a210b3","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用支那銀行 唔食曬你結餘咪算好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你返工你間公司係要出糧去佢公司銀行嘅戶口，你係咪一定 唔撚柒返嗰份工同 立刻辭職? (我本身係用恆生銀行)"},{"pid":"58f4018f7b6536106f80feb27f979ba811326340","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇keep張receipt?有就去counter同佢講翻！之前係HS試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc273000987ac7b58ac0a9cdbc7d40c972bccab5","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:54:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都要驚<br />\n係咪鄉下落黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你咪試下囉，你啱啱出糧嗰日畀人扣咗錢，睇下你驚唔驚， 香港樣樣都係錢， 又要供樓又要食， 你係咪香港人就真"},{"pid":"42401996ec536ddd2bf729c622724edaf852722d","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公眾假期聽電話d人好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次俾佢食簿，但我第二日就離開hk有排唔返，打過去係個c9，乜都唔知個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係真係好仆街，同埋好廢，來來去去都係嗰幾句"},{"pid":"62b53b07b31268d812a5f4c94c2d4782a44b5a91","tid":185914,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">999？屌你老母部櫃員機食撚左我錢！</span>"},{"pid":"3b5a031921ef6ecf9467b65ae7779dffced93c61","tid":185914,"uid":5252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"試過食左我9000 打電話去問 銀行話等部櫃員機無曬錢既時候佢地一對數就會睇到 叫我唔洗擔心<br />\n<br />\n過兩日就打比我話已經退返入我戶口"},{"pid":"8967d915c2e3246869834cba54531787b4c8952e","tid":185914,"uid":96069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"星期三去分行大堂填表得架啦，一兩個星期會比番你<br />\n利申中銀櫃員"},{"pid":"5c317881e4c12f0a25723e9be30ab1a166b9807c","tid":185914,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dcd111603fbcc6d7eed077b35f327a97f9c59053","tid":185914,"uid":4405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"我試過 中銀好多機都會咁<br />\n撳錢前睇下佢是咪得返100蚊紙出<br />\n如果係 你又撳成6000 唔知係佢出唔到60張<br />\n定係唔夠 會唔出 但又照扣<br />\n打返去銀行做remark就大約一星期到比返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17fc95d7f15da9acc85505d3dcd02d0ee667c3f","tid":185914,"uid":23110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"正確方法：上連登問巴打<br />\n錯誤方法：即時打去中銀講一聲位置機身編號"},{"pid":"aba32d5df5424e964e2a5ff7f66c28ad0185e4da","tid":185914,"uid":71949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正確方法：上連登問巴打<br />\n錯誤方法：即時打去中銀講一聲位置機身編號</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一早做咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早都話打咗去問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇睇文㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dec8f53c16091c78c57e6d8075fc1c0754a2688","tid":185914,"uid":85405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:46:20.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"089165d98f50101d368027e0edd6c7b4932c7257","tid":185914,"uid":50428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:48:14.000Z","msg":"試過 我一個學生仔吞鳩我幾百蚊。<br />\n我專登望一望cctv 記番邊部機幾點拎錢 好似幾日有番"}]}